data.description: Enjoy low maintenance living in this 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home offering an open floor plan, over 2600 square feet, First floor primary with ensuite, 10' ceilings downstairs, gourmet kitchen with huge center island, office, laundry room, and cozy family room with fireplace. Lots of upgrades in this beautiful home! Just minutes to Colonial Williamsburg, William and Mary, shopping, dining and entertainment.
